nodes.name: Scion
nodes.description: The Scion - All paths begin here

nodes.name: Resolute Technique
nodes.description: Your hits can't be Evaded. Never deal Critical Strikes

nodes.name: Blood Magic
nodes.description: Removes all Mana. Spend Life instead of Mana for Skills. +30% more Maximum Life

nodes.name: Chaos Inoculation
nodes.description: Maximum Life becomes 1. Immune to Chaos Damage. +60% more Energy Shield

nodes.name: Elemental Equilibrium
nodes.description: Enemies you hit with Elemental Damage temporarily get +25% Resistance to those Elements and -50% to others

nodes.name: Pain Attunement
nodes.description: 30% more Spell Damage when on Low Life

nodes.name: Iron Reflexes
nodes.description: Converts all Evasion Rating to Armour. Dexterity provides no bonus to Evasion Rating

nodes.name: Acrobatics
nodes.description: +30% Chance to Dodge Attack Hits. 30% less Armour and Energy Shield

nodes.name: Avatar of Fire
nodes.description: Deal no Non-Fire Damage. 50% of Physical, Lightning and Cold Damage Converted to Fire Damage

nodes.name: Unwavering Stance
nodes.description: Cannot Evade enemy Attacks. Cannot be Stunned
